Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be your boyfriend,\Nbut I can act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my hardest to make you love me.\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'll arrange for her to meet L.\NShe'll tell me his name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I eliminate\Nthe entire Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that's done,\NI'll kill her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the only person\Nwho knows Kira's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one.\NI can't let her live much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'll just pretend?\NAll right. I guess it's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've talked about that,\Ncould you show me your Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanna see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I need her to trust me,\NI guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a completely different type\Nof Shinigami than Rem, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know your name.\NIt's Ryuk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way, Light darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know how to kill a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Did you just call me "darling"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Then, do you mind\Nif I call you "Knight" instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're like my knight\Nin shining armor, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Let's just stick with Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] So, were you actually\Nplanning to check all of the footage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we got from Aoyama on the 22nd\Nby yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I think it's very likely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira and the Second Kira made contact\Nwith each other there on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to check\Nall of these tapes personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Also, Mr. Yagami?\N-Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ask Mr. Mogi\Nto start following Light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can keep tabs on what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] You want him followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a slim chance,\Nbut if Light is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then, there's still a possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that the second Kira might try\Nto contact him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Very well.\N-[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to wonder\Nif Ryuzaki is even human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy never sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him sleeping in that\Nexact same position the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh.\N-[Matsuda] No, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if a Shinigami has feelings\Nfor a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and kills someone else\Nin order to extend that human's life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond its natural end,\Nthe Shinigami will die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck trying to find a Shinigami\Nwho'd volunteer to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see you ever doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where did you send\Nall those tapes from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that went to the TV stations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Osaka, the first time.\NThen Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This other one from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the bullet train every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so that way the police couldn't pinpoint\Nmy location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one more thing.\NDo you still have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the video tapes and envelopes\Nwith your friend's fingerprints on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll have to dispose of everything\Nthat was used to create those video tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But before you do,\NI need you to send one last video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure it's from a place\Nyou haven't used yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've decided to stop searching for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to thank\Nthe police department
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of its advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I still plan to help Kira\Nin his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope that in time,\Nhe'll come to see me as an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will start by punishing criminals\Nthat Kira has yet to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will share my power with others\Nwho I feel are worthy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will encourage them to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll make this world\Na better place."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Share my power"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just add that part\Nto throw off their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They suspect that there are already\Ntwo people with this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so it wouldn't be a stretch to assume\Nthere could be others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they believe the numbers are\Ngrowing, then they'll start to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to ask.\NJust tell me what to do and I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is\Nbecause I'd do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] There's one more thing\Nwhich is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get arrested by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're ever brought in\Nfor questioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you can never mention anything\Nabout us or the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they don't get a hold\Nof that notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no proof that you did anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise to say nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So this must mean that we're officially\Nboyfriend and girlfriend now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'd like to add one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go on a date with me\Nat least once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]\NUnbelievable. She still doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can't.\N-[gasps] But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, it looks like I'm gonna have\Nto spell this out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,L already suspects that I'm Kira,\Ndo you see what I'm saying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! L is amazing.\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been saying that he's getting\Nnowhere with the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he's a complete idiot and stuff.\NBut he already knows that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's all worked out well for me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because thanks to that,\NI've also been able to get close to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You and L are\Nin contact with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that's even more amazing.\NThis is getting so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he suspects I'm Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,L figures he's safe as long as\NI don't know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He came right out and told me who he was,\Njust to get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he's only focusing on me\Nbecause he has no other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At this moment,\NI'm working with him on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And little by little,\NI'm winning his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. So all you have to do\Nis take me to where L is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can see his real name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] I'm afraid it's not that simple.\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, it was difficult enough for me\Nto get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if all of a sudden,\Nsomeone I just met gets too close,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the same time,\Nthe police detect changes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in Kira or the Second Kira's behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that person will be suspected\Nof being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, that will put me\Nunder even greater suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't allow them to make\Nthat connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we can't appear\Nto be too close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is that why we can't go on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be seen in public\Nbecause it will look too suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take the time now\Nto come up with a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some way that you can see L\Nwithout letting him know you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I can't eliminate L without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll call you and see you\Nas often as this situation allows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] But...\N-[Misa] Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,... to make sure that our meetings\Ndon't stand out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure that I'm seen\Nwith other girls, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seriously going to date\Nother girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-[yelling] I don't want you to.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see you with another girl,\NI'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, sweetie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sweetie"? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us are risking our lives\Nto change the world, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, but...\NI love you more than the world, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it feels that way to you,\Nbut you're here because you admire Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know me.\NWe just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you believe in love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit that everything you said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did want to meet Kira out of gratitude\Nand respect, not love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the moment I first saw you,\NI knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What is wrong with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Popular as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can show me your love\Nby obeying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said it was okay\Nif I used you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A minute ago, you swore\Nyou'd do anything I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did. But I never said\Nyou could date other girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, those are two totally\Ndifferent things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're forgetting\NI have both notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't obey me,\NI can easily kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] I would never allow that,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do anything\Nthat results in this girl's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing I'll do is write your name\Nin my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you realize\Nthat I can see her lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If she happens to die before that time,\NI'll know it was you who killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] But if you were to use\Nyour Death Note to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that mean you die, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. If you try to save me,\Nyou would die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm quite willing\Nto accept that outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Is this Shinigami serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-And this means, from now on--\N-[knocking on door]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Sachiko] Light?\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost 11:30, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't have a girl here\Nthis late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mrs. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I'm really sorry\Nfor coming over so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-See you later, Light .\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, you should walk her to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I can't risk being seen with her\Nin public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. No, I'm all right, thanks.\NWell, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. When she got here,\NI wasn't so sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're right, she's cute, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That Shinigami is going to kill me\Nif I kill that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means... I'm going to have her\Nhanging around me until she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It also means\Nthat I'll be forced to protect her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from being caught by the police\Nfor the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Rem, Light really is\Ngoing to be my knight in shining armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] But you can't really kill him,\Nokay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Shinigami to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to use their Death Note\Nto save the life of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A human whom they have\Nfallen in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally, I could kill Rem first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone I was controlling\Nwould attack Misa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,forcing Rem to save her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would never work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If Misa's life was put in danger,\NRem would immediately suspect me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd be the one who'd get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] As things stand,\Nshe's a bigger nuisance than L is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] She's-- She's famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I don't even want to imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen\Nif someone found out about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! She's nothing but trouble.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No. More importantly, I need to think\Nof how I can use Misa's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to help me kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can eliminate him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Good morning, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Sayu,\Ncould you do me a big favor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep Misa a secret\Nfrom Dad for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not just Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell anyone else\Nabout her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Misa's an up-and-coming model\Nso people can't know about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is she really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was pretty\Nbut I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty impressive,\Neven for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it a secret... for 50 bucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Sachiko] Oh, stop it.\N-[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,TO-OH UNIVERSITY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, on page 246...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NMisa's final message should arrive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, before it ever gets\Nto the TV station,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be rerouted\Nto Task Force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go down there at some point\Nso I can see L's reaction first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl] Light. Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you and I were\Nseeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, we're more than\Njust friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. And that's the reason why\NI'm sitting next to you in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-wouldn't you agree?\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't look like\Nyou enjoy being with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,\Nyou haven't even looked at me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was just thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how everyone's going to be talking\Nabout us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I'm actually going out with\NMiss Takada, the famous Miss Todai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're the most beautiful woman\Nat the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat] Why do you even care\Nabout stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I hate being called Miss Todai,\Nor whatever. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What do you know,\Nshe actually likes all the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should forget about all that stuff\Nand just go at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come in. Your timing\Ncouldn't be better, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We just received a new video message\Nfrom the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wow, that didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes.\NI believe it's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Second Kira]\NI've decided to stop searching for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to thank\Nthe police department for their advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I still plan to help Kira\Nin his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope that in time,\Nhe will come to see me as an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will start by punishing criminals\Nthat Kira has yet to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I will share my power with others\Nwho I feel are worthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will encourage them\Nto do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll make this world\Na better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] After watching this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only think that Kira and\Nthe Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,have managed to make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. Didn't you sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you'd come to\Nthe same conclusion I did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,after watching this one through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First, consider how determined he was\Nto meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So why the sudden change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he wants to punish criminals\Nthat Kira hasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All he wants out of it is for Kira\Nto see him as an ally? [swallows]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It begs the question,\Nwhy didn't he do this to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing it's because he never thought\Nthat far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably met Kira and was told\Nwhich criminals he'd be allowed to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect the purpose of this message\Nis to hide the fact that they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I find really strange is\Nthat it's unlike Kira to be so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. But are we to believe\Nthat Kira made a mistake this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this his way of letting us know\Nthat they made contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be an effective means\Nof provoking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of their union\Nis very threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this is also one less reason\Nto suspect that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Ryuzaki,\Nwhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Light is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this is the message\Nhe would have had the Second Kira send us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have made the Second Kira\Ngo through with his plan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to have me appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, deny that they ever made contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,letting the Second Kira shoulder the blame\Nfor my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd make him say something like, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Although I agreed not to go through\Nwith this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to realize that it was\Nnot Kira's true intention that I stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive that the real Kira\Nwould want L to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd make me stop."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Ryuzaki.\N-Yes, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're mistaken.\NI would never do that if I were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're L and I'm Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'd already know your personality\Npretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,L would never agree to appear on TV,\Nno matter what threat he was facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wouldn't allow someone else to die\Nin his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The L I know would find some way\Nto escape the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Light, you've got to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like hearing you say,\N"If I were Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let Ryuzaki know\Nexactly what I thought of his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I posed that scenario because\NI want to help solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only chance I have\Nto clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the only reason\NI feel comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,saying things like that\Nis because I'm not really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, it would be a problem\Nif you were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... [sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you're the first friend\Nthat I have ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.\NThe two of us have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have missed having you around\Nat school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We should play tennis again, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?\NHe's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good thing, isn't it, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Ryuzaki,\Nhe had no problem figuring out Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Second Kira had made contact\Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-I've got to eliminate him right away.\N-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The way things are progressing,\NI can't afford to be seen with Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa yells] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light grunts]\N-I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just couldn't wait for two weeks\Nlike you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was just on my way to\Nyour house when I spotted you. [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This is the first time in my life\Nthat I've been provoked to hit a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just wanted to see you so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you might as well come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Another girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great to see you Misa.\NI saw you in a whole bunch of magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please, come on in.\N-[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop by like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you make us some tea, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Rem.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Misa's ally, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd seen her many times\Nfrom the Shinigami realm, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,certain events made me develop feelings\Nfor her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings? But you're a Shinigami?\N[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like what I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,about how I'd kill you\Nif you even attempted to kill Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Misa is happy, does that mean\Nthat you'll be happy as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't want her to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] As you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Misa.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was happy,\Nwould that make you happy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Misa] Yes.\N-[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Rem said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that your happiness was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you think would happen\Nif L caught one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It means our happiness would be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] It's true\Nthat Shinigami are forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to give out a person's name\Nto anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again, there's no rule\Nthat prevents Rem from killing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NAnd if you agree to kill L,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it would only make me love Misa\Nthat much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I'd be grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Most importantly, the two of us\Nwould be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem.\NI want Light to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know we could be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Light Yagami.\NBut I do not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This will not kill me, even if it ends up\Nlengthening your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill L for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes no difference.\NHe is just another human to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rem, thank you so much.\NI knew I could count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,L will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it took?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]